"""
    Test SS.SS_fsolve function.  Provide inputs to function and
    ensure that output returned matches what it has been before.
    """
test_list = SS.SS_fsolve(guesses, *args)
assert np.allclose(np.array(test_list), np.array(expected), atol=1e-06)
pytest.mark.parametrize('guesses,args,expected', [(guesses1, args1,
    expected1), (guesses2, args2, expected2), (guesses3, args3, expected3),
    (guesses4, args4, expected4), (guesses5, args5, expected5), (guesses6,
    args6, expected6)], ids=['Baseline, Closed', 'Reform, Closed',
    'Reform, Baseline spending=True, Closed', 'Baseline, Partial Open',
    'Baseline, Small Open', 'Baseline, Closed, delta_tau = 0'])
